      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison against FDA experimental benchmark at 2500 RPM, 5 L/min",
      "description": "Simulated velocity magnitudes compared to particle image velocimetry measurements from the FDA benchmark dataset. Mean absolute error 8.3% across measurement planes; peak shear stress regions show systematic under-prediction of 12–18%, contributing to the gap in Output Comparison credibility factor."
