    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-index-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Normalized index of hemolysis comparison across 5 operating points",
      "description": "Predicted NIH values compared to in-vitro hemolysis measurements at matched flow-speed conditions. Model over-predicts hemolysis by a factor of 1.4–2.1 depending on operating point. Uncertainty bands from Monte Carlo UQ do not fully enclose experimental values at two of five operating points, indicating model form error beyond quantified parametric uncertainty."
    }
