    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors evaluated. Seven factors assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors not assessed, flagged as epistemic gaps. The hemolysis power-law model form relies on constants from a correlation study (Giersiepen et al.) cited via external reference; that bibliographic node is not resolved within this package. Output comparison factor shows systematic over-prediction of 40–110%. Monte Carlo UQ is incomplete. Overall credibility is insufficient for Class III regulatory submission at MRL 5. Decision: Not accepted.",
